{"tid":1123981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"識好多廢中只買春，唔拍拖、唔結婚","createTime":"2019-04-24T19:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T02:23:38.000Z","uid":82929,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a927824426af8fc21b0dd3d350d3adc2da75753f","tid":1123981,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T19:25:08.000Z","msg":"曾經當佢地係一個笑話、係一堆垃圾雞蟲<br />\n<br />\n過左咁多年，今日終於明左，原來佢地先係智者。唔係個個都配有感情，買春真係一個高性價比宣洩渠道<br />\n<br />\n明白依個道理代價實在太大，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早5年發現就唔會浪費咁多時間係到搵感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8fb2da7711dc6177b4f40beeef169aecc5e005","tid":1123981,"uid":82929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T20:03:31.000Z","msg":"毒撚遠離情情愛愛，其實真係會活得更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9331ac13dabd486dede77853495e861e3b5c1acf","tid":1123981,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:21:24.000Z","msg":"唔係個個配有感情，依句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a820884f28b6fd9b0af9570847023bac19250e90","tid":1123981,"uid":187544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:26:39.000Z","msg":"咩都假，有錢就咩都有（除健康），家人或親人之類，有錢就算身邊一人都無，外面一樣有大把豬朋狗友，就算想人陪，日日搵唔同女訓都得，錢多。"},{"pid":"d4771f94c34da57b50c30660dd24317ae456bac3","tid":1123981,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a820884f28b6fd9b0af9570847023bac19250e90","tid":1123981,"uid":187544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:26:39.000Z","msg":"咩都假，有錢就咩都有（除健康），家人或親人之類，有錢就算身邊一人都無，外面一樣有大把豬朋狗友，就算想人陪，日日搵唔同女訓都得，錢多。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:35:28.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"